{"blogid": "126741872", "writerAge": "码龄148天", "writerBlogNum": "488", "writerCollect": "0", "writerComment": "0", "writerFan": "63", "writerGrade": "6级", "writerIntegral": "5180", "writerName": "XYBMWCR", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_126741872.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "5612", "writerRankWeekly": "7791", "writerThumb": "0", "writerVisitNum": "18130", "blog_read_count": "14", "blog_time": "于 2022-09-07 11:29:21 发布", "blog_title": "吲哚菁绿（ICG）一种近红外I区荧光染料", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p>吲哚菁绿（ICG）是一种近红外I区荧光染料[1]，是美国食品药品监督管理局（FDA）批准的体内应用染料。其激发和发射波长分别在785 nm、810 nm左右，比Cy系列（花菁类）染料（630-670 nm、650-700 nm）更长，可穿透更深的活体组织。</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\e8023e04bd0aa1822a8e2165cf42674b.png\"/></p>\n<p>图1 tumour比周围组织吸收更多ICG，证实ICG可更好地用于tumour细胞体内成像</p>\n<p>[1]</p>\n<p>有研究表明，tumour比其他组织吸收更多ICG，当ICG注射到tumour附近时，tumour对光的反应是周围组织2.5倍（图1）[2]，另外通过将ICG与抗体结合，也可以靶向特定细胞。</p>\n<p>ICG及其衍生物主要应用领域包括：（1）眼科blood vessel造影；（2）组织和器官的灌注诊断；（3）tumour的前哨淋巴结活检；（4）近红外荧光/光声双模态成像；（5）光动力/光热treatment协同treatment[1-4]。</p>\n<p> 相关产品</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\03b6f6a424189c47db07e47c03035d87.png\"/></p>\n<p>181934-09-8</p>\n<p>ICG-COOH, 95%</p>\n<p>吲哚菁绿羧酸</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\41d331ea00508e405871b282f3796b76.png\"/></p>\n<p>1622335-40-3</p>\n<p>ICG-NHS, 95%</p>\n<p>吲哚菁绿琥珀酰亚胺酯</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\3142c3eae98515432db82273b9c512ce.png\"/></p>\n<p>2143933-81-5</p>\n<p>ICG-Maleimide, 95%</p>\n<p>吲哚菁绿马来酰亚胺</p>\n<p>ICG-Tetrazine, 95%</p>\n<p>吲哚菁绿四嗪</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\1716f1c09d86d2dd16337197318d69df.png\"/></p>\n<p>ICG-azide, 95%</p>\n<p>吲哚菁绿叠氮</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\f1ec8a899c2d6d80ab8deb21765798fd.png\"/></p>\n<p>1622335-41-4</p>\n<p>ICG-alkyne, 95%</p>\n<p>吲哚菁绿炔